    print(signup.password)
```

Or:

```python
def create_user(user_data: CreateStructure):
    print(user_data.name)
    print(user_data.password)
```

Both still work.

The matching rule is:

```text
HTTP JSON keys must match the Pydantic model fields.
The function parameter name can be whatever you want.
```

So this works:

```python
